    <item>
      <title>新研究发现，Z 世代选民反对社交媒体限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/gen-z-voters-oppose-social-media-limits-new-voter-study-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项对 430 名首次投票者的民意调查显示，美国青少年普遍反对限制他们使用社交媒体平台的规定，尽管他们知道这可能会对身心健康造成危害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/gen-z-voters-oppose-social-media-limits-new-voter-study-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 19:43:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国政局动荡表明保皇派仍在掌权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thai-political-upheaval-shows-royalists-still-firmly-in-charge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国领导人上任不到一年就被赶下台，这清楚地表明了一件事：过去二十年来，在军方支持下长期实行统治的保皇派政权仍然掌握着全部权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thai-political-upheaval-shows-royalists-still-firmly-in-charge</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
